 -->\n<h5>CRM Systems</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Write textâ¦\"} -->\n<p>Improve your customer engagement with a bespoke, secure and dedicated CRM system <br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:getwid/image-box --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"className\":\"has-3-columns\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns has-3-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:getwid/image-box {\"id\":44,\"textAlignment\":\"left\",\"mobileLayout\":\"column\",\"mobileAlignment\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-image-box has-text-left has-mobile-layout-column has-mobile-alignment-center\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-image-box__image-container is-position-top\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-image-box__image-wrapper\"><img src=\"https://getwid.getmotopress.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/icons_service4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-block-getwid-image-box__image wp-image-44\"/></div></div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-image-box__content\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5,\"placeholder\":\"Write headingâ¦\"} -->\n<h5>Startup Software</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Write textâ¦\"} -->\n<p>We help startups and ventures with the most challenging tech aspect of starting a project</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:getwid/image-box --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:getwid/image-box {\"id\":40,\"textAlignment\":\"left\",\"mobileLayout\":\"column\",\"mobileAlignment\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-image-box has-text-left has-mobile-layout-column has-mobile-alignment-center\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-image-box__image-container is-position-top\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-image-box__image-wrapper\"><img src=\"https://getwid.getmotopress.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/icons_service5.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-block-getwid-image-box__image wp-image-40\"/></div></div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-image-box__content\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5,\"placeholder\":\"Write headingâ¦\"} -->\n<h5>White Label</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Write textâ¦\"} -->\n<p>We can help you build white label software solutions that you can license to your own clients </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:getwid/image-box --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:getwid/image-box {\"id\":45,\"textAlignment\":\"left\",\"mobileLayout\":\"column\",\"mobileAlignment\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-image-box has-text-left has-mobile-layout-column has-mobile-alignment-center\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-image-box__image-container is-position-top\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-image-box__image-wrapper\"><img src=\"https://getwid.getmotopress.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/icons_service6.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-block-getwid-image-box__image wp-image-45\"/></div></div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-image-box__content\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5,\"placeholder\":\"Write headingâ¦\"} -->\n<h5>Consultancy</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Write textâ¦\"} -->\n<p>Our software consultants help define technology barriers to improve business tech aspects </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:getwid/image-box --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div></div></div></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:getwid/section -->\n\n<!-- wp:getwid/section {\"align\":\"full\",\"skipLayout\":true,\"contentMaxWidthPreset\":\"custom\",\"contentMaxWidth\":1600,\"gapSize\":\"\",\"backgroundImagePosition\":\"bottom left\",\"backgroundImageSize\":\"auto\",\"paddingRightValue\":\"50%\",\"paddingLeft\":\"large\",\"paddingRight\":\"large\",\"paddingLeftMobile\":\"medium\",\"paddingRightMobile\":\"medium\",\"className\":\"alignfull\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section alignfull getw